31 SECTION 4. Section 8C of Chapter 40 of the General Laws, as so appearing, is hereby
32 amended by inserting at the end thereof the following new paragraph:-
33 The members of the commission shall complete such training programs conducted or
34 sponsored by the department of environmental protection under the provisions of Section 15A of
35 Chapter 21A prior to their service on the commission.
36 SECTION 5. Section 12 of Chapter 40A of the General Laws, as so appearing, is hereby
37 amended by inserting at the end thereof the following new paragraph:-
