39 by the department of housing and community development under the provisions of Section 3 of
40 Chapter 23B prior to their service on the board.
41 SECTION 6. Section 81A of Chapter 41 of the General Laws, as so appearing, is hereby
42 amended by inserting at the end thereof the following new paragraph:-
43 The members of the board shall complete such training programs conducted or sponsored
44 by the department of housing and community development under the provisions of Section 3 of
45 Chapter 23B prior to their service on the board.
46 SECTION 7. Section 26 of Chapter 111 of the General Laws, as so appearing, is hereby
47 amended by inserting after the fifth sentence the following new sentence:- The members of the
48 board shall complete such training programs conducted or sponsored by the department of public
49 health under the provisions of Section 7B of Chapter 17 prior to their service on the board.
